warning=This plugin uploads your account data and activity to osrsbestinslot.com, keyed by a link token you paste. It submits your IP address; your skills, quests, achievement diaries, equipment, inventory and bank contents (to auto-fill the calculators); and your account activity — completed trades including the other player's name and the items each side traded, items you loot from kills, Grand Exchange and shop transactions, deaths, level-ups, and login times. If you enable trade screenshots it also uploads screenshots of your trade window, which show the other player's name. Only enable it if you are comfortable with all of that being uploaded.
